{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "两位造物主 第21章 3-3 因为爱着世界",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "面对掌管所有魔力的圣域龙，\\n一行人陷入苦战，危机之中\\n王子通过“临化”摆脱危机\\n并最终打倒了圣域龙。正当晓之圣片\\n即将到手之际，塞西娅却突然出手阻挠。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "唔呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "厉害……\\n上一个伤到我的人\\n还是阿尔贝琉斯吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "回想起来……自那之后\\n我就再也没有对可能性\\n这种东西抱有期待了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "这个世界因他而踏上了改革之路。\\n我也幻想过那条路也许\\n最终能阻止世界走向毁灭。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "既然如此，圣域龙！\\n能不能再给我们……\\n再给人类一次机会呢！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我给过你们机会。在众多世界里，\\n给过你们无数次机会……\\n然而，很遗憾这一切都是徒劳。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "因为在阿尔贝琉斯建国之后的世界里，\\n世界毁灭的导火索往往\\n就是阿尔贝里亚王室的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "伊莉雅……阿尔贝琉斯……\\n他们都是值得\\n被称为英雄的人物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "但是，只要他们还在追求可能性，\\n就会连他们的存在也无法\\n让世界脱离走向毁灭的轨道。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就算是这样，今后也许\\n会出现比伊莉雅和阿尔贝琉斯\\n更加出色的英雄啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这也是因为拥有可能性\\n才会有的期待吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我早已放弃了等待。\\n经历过无数次毁灭之后，\\n我不认为等待有任何价值。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎、怎么这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "别尝试无谓的沟通了。\\n事已至此，你以为圣域龙\\n会回心转意吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "眼下要做的就是制服圣域龙，\\n得到晓之圣片，仅此而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "唉……果然阿尔贝琉斯的\\n后人依然会选择迈上\\n通往毁灭的阶梯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这与阿尔贝琉斯无关。\\n我只是想凭自己的意愿打倒你，\\n将这个世界从扭曲的支配中解放出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "很遗憾，这不可能。\\n就凭你们是无法打败我的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我还不至于看不出来\\n你已经是强弩之末。\\n只差最后一击，一切都将尘埃落定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "不，只要这个世界的魔力\\n还由我掌管，就不可能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "接受我的制裁吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "怎么……回事！？\\n身、身体动不了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "圣域龙！\\n你到底……做了什么！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "你们忘了这个世界的\\n魔力是由我掌管的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "是我暂停了魔力的活动。\\n你们应该连动一下\\n都做不到了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "这可……不太妙……\\n就算只有奈迪犹一个人也好……\\n得让他逃走才行……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芩……你的力量\\n还够一次“临化”吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "你要做什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "只要利用不受\\n圣域龙支配的魔力，\\n就能打破现状。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "不受圣域龙支配的魔力……\\n原来如此……我懂了……\\n我来……试试看！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "把那家伙的魔力引出来……\\n唔啊啊啊啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "唔……对不起，奈迪犹……\\n我的力量似乎已经透支了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "行不通吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（这……漂浮起来的魔力……\\n原来如此，我知道奈迪犹\\n想怎么做了！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（既然“临化”\\n是龙化的一种……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（因为契约而连接的魔力流向……\\n不是去捕捉魔力的流向进行龙化，\\n而是要吸收漂浮起来的魔力！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "什么！？\\n王子他竟然“临化”了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "展开“虚面领域”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "身体能动了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "趁现在！奈迪犹！各位！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "不用你说！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "啊、啊啊啊啊啊！\\n我必须……要保护……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你试图保护的存在\\n追求着你所否定的可能性。\\n这种矛盾就是你犯的错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我……世界……人类……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "沉睡吧，圣域龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210161_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我、我们……赢了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "应该是吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "没想到……\\n我竟然会亲手打倒\\n崇拜至今的圣域龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "即使是神，\\n一旦放弃就注定没有未来，\\n就是这么简单的道理。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣树",
            "context": "这话还真是残酷呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣树",
            "context": "你们明白圣域龙的爱有多深，\\n以及他的失望和绝望吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣树",
            "context": "在无限时光中不断上演的毁灭；\\n无论爱得有多深\\n都终将消失的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣树",
            "context": "你们所知道的不过是\\n漫长岁月中的一刹那，为何能否定\\n他在经历过一切后做出的决断呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "或许是这样没错……\\n我们发现圣域龙才是对的\\n那一天也许终将到来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但我们依然愿意相信可能性，\\n哪怕它极其微小。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣树",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这不是圣域龙\\n对与错的问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "只是我们很难接受而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "好了，圣树，\\n交出晓之圣片吧——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣树",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_05_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
